Package: deva.ai
Title: Virginia Environmental Inequality Calculator
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jonathan", "Ogebe", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package uses a combination of US Census data and NEI data from the US EPA to calculate environmental inequity across racial/ethnic groups in the state of Virginia from 2011 to 2020. The environmental inequity measures used are the Atkinson Index and the Gini coefficient.
